Citation.sTitle: Refractive Indices of Lithium, Magnesium, and Copper(II) Sulfates in Ethanol-Water Solutions
Citation.sAbstract: The refractive indices of lithium, magnesium and copper sulphates in ethanol + water solutions were measured at the temperature range (288.15 to 318.15 K) and atmospheric pressure. Also ethanol + water and single salt + water binary systems were measured. Binary and Ternary systems were correlated using polynomial expressions, parameters depend on composition of mixtures. Data fitting shows a good agreement with experimental values.
